<subSubSection pageId="29" pageNumber="628" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="29.[170,1379,1236,1896]" pageId="29" pageNumber="628">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[171,529,1746,1780]" pageId="29" pageNumber="628">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. Botta’s Gerbil is considered quite rare; few preserved specimens are known.
</paragraph>
